page.title: 09INDUSTRY IN HOUNSLOW (1)
page.content: Industry is about people and work. {Industry}can be classified into{three} {sectors. Primary}sector consists of workers who extract raw materials from the earth's resources. {Secondary} industries consist of manufacturers. {Tertiary}industries consist of people who provide services for the community. Inorder to make a study of industry in Hounslow a questionaire was circulated among 50 people in Hounslow. The results of this questionaire are as follows: Airline manager based at Heathrow Airport Company director Security man Plasterer/builder (2) School master Office Clerk (5) Photographer
